<div id="toc-list">
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc0">1: Howdy!</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc1">2: &quot;What You See Is What You Get.&quot;</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc2">3: &quot;Logs&quot;</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc3">4: &quot;Logical Extremes&quot;</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc4">5: &quot;Subversion&quot;</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc5">6: &quot;Further Notes On Things That Do A Thing&quot;</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1em;"><a href="#toc6">7: &quot;TL;DR&quot;</a></div>
</div>
</div>
